      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and always parked under cover. You won't find a single scratch or blemish anywhere. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and I'm only letting it go because I'm downsizing. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
