    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E30 M3 featuring the iconic S14 inline-four engine with its high-compression head and individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 265 dog-leg manual transmission and a factory 25% locking limited-slip differential, both of which operate with surgical precision. This example boasts a pristine chassis with all original VIN tags intact and a suspension geometry refreshed with period-correct Bilstein dampers. The mechanical assembly is dry, showing no signs of seepage or subframe fatigue. A meticulously preserved specimen that delivers the raw, analog feedback essential to the homologation-special experience.",
      "price": 44500.0,
