    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this car\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it still has that brand-new feel. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition, inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and looks totally flawless, this is the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
