    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the robust 3.8L MA1.01 DFI flat-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, delivering 385 hp with a linear power band and no IMS bearing vulnerabilities. The vehicle is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a mechanical limited-slip differential, providing exceptional lateral grip and turn-in response. Condition is superlative: the body panels show factory-spec tolerances with original paint depth throughout, and the undercarriage remains free of oxidation with factory cosmoline still visible. A recent DME interrogation confirms a clean rev history with zero over-revs in ranges 2 through 6. The hydraulic steering rack is bone-dry, and the suspension bushings retain their factory-fresh elasticity, ensuring a communicative and vibration-free chassis. This is a turn-key, investment-quality example for the discerning purist.",
